comments: Rozier (CHA) makes incidental foot contact with his teammate Biyombo (CHA) which affects his SQBR.
Graham (CHA) commits a take foul on Garland (CLE).
Thompson (CLE) is firming up and make marginal contact with Biyombo (CHA) as he sets the screen.
Biyombo (CHA) is firming up and makes marginal contact with Sexton (CLE) during the screen.
Rozier (CHA) takes fewer than three steps after he has gathered the ball.
Rozier (CHA) makes slight contact with Sexton (CLE) during his drive that does not affect his defensive position.
Graham (CHA) jumps from point A to point B and makes contact with Garland (CLE) that affects his driving shot attempt.
Garland (CLE) briefly engages with Biyombo's (CHA) body after the screen is set.
Biyombo (CHA) is firming up and makes marginal contact with Garland (CLE) during the pick.
Sexton (CLE) slightly extends off arm into the upper body of Rozier (CHA) during the drive.
Rozier (CHA) makes marginal contact to the body of Sexton (CLE) during his shooting motion that does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Osman (CLE) commits a take foul on Biyombo (CHA).
Osman (CLE) commits a take foul on Graham (CHA).
Charlotte is rewarded a timeout prior to throwing the ball out of bounds.
Sexton (CLE) commits a take foul on Rozier (CHA).
